# Root .dockerignore — applies to every `docker build` in this repo since all
# three Dockerfiles (apps/api-gateway, apps/generation-worker, apps/web) use
# the repo root as build context (see docs/deployment.md). Keeps images small
# and, critically, keeps secrets out of build contexts/layers.

# VCS / tooling
.git
.github
.claude
.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.mypy_cache
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache

# Docs / specs — not needed inside images
docs
README.md
LICENSE

# IaC — irrelevant to application image builds
infra/terraform
infra/k8s
infra/cloudrun

# Node — reinstalled fresh inside the web image; never trust a host node_modules
**/node_modules
**/.next
apps/web/e2e
apps/web/playwright-report
apps/web/test-results

# Secrets — never let a stray local .env end up in a build context/layer
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
